# The benchmarks image is DEPS-ONLY. Only _deps/ (package-manager manifests) and
# .cacerts/ are COPYed into the image; everything else is bind-mounted at run time
# (see scripts/benchmarks.sh:mount_args) and must stay OUT of the build context.
# NOTE: these patterns are anchored at the context root, so `competitors/` etc.
# exclude the top-level source dirs but NOT their _deps/ manifest mirrors.

# Generated / host-only — never enter the image build context.
**/node_modules
**/dist
.vite
results/
.image-stamp
.git/
*.log
*.tgz

# First-party benchmark source/config — bind-mounted at run time, never baked.
shared/
competitors/
typecost/
aggregate.mjs
tsconfig.base.json
README.md
